-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Adecco, SocGen
-- 
-- Thu Dec 11, 2014 12:31AM EST
-- None



Dec 11 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Deutsche Bank and Adecco, on Thursday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Staffing: Jefferies downgrades Adecco <ADEN.VX>; upgrades Hays <HAYS.L> [ID:nWNAB05H2J] * Banks: Jefferies cuts target on Deutsche Bank <DBKGn.DE>, SocGen <SOGN.PA>Following is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Thursday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * Adecco <ADEN.VX>: Jefferies cuts to underperform from hold * Adecco <ADEN.VX>: Jefferies cuts price target to Sfr 58 from Sfr 73.5 * Deutsche Bank <DBKGn.DE>: Jefferies cuts target to 37 euros from 38 euros; rating buy * Hays <HAYS.L>: Jefferies raises to buy from hold * Hays <HAYS.L>: Jefferies raises price target to 180p from 165p * Michael Page <MPI.L>: Jefferies cuts price target to 430p from 500p; rating hold * Randstad <RAND.AS>: Jefferies cuts price target to 39 euros from 46.5 euros; rating hold * Severfield Plc <SFR.L>: Jefferies raises price target to 71 from 66p; rating buy * Societe Generale <SOGN.PA>: Jefferies cuts target to 42 euros from 45 euros; rating hold * SThree <STHR.L>: Jefferies raises to buy from hold; cuts price target to 370p from 450p * Telecity Group <TCY.L>: Evercore ISI raises price target to 825p from 800p; rating hold